                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9970" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">OB-0441</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2045 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行随“境”变：管理者角色变化如何助推在芙山房的发展</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Adaptation to the Environment: How the Transformation of the Management Roles Facilitates the Development of Zai fu shan fang</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">杨慧，李泽宇</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">江西财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在芙山房民宿（江西山言旅游发展有限公司）</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">18 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在芙山房；民宿；管理者角色；文化传承；乡村振兴；2025百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Zai Fu Shan Fang, Homestay, Management roles, Cultural inheritance, Rural Revitalization</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">摘要：随着中国乡村振兴战略深入推进，乡村旅游与民宿产业成为激活乡村经济、传承传统文化的重要载体。在此背景下，本文通过分析江西南昌“在芙山房”民宿主理人韩莉的管理实践，探讨其如何通过多阶段战略转型，实现在芙山房从单一民宿到新业态民宿村落的蜕变。在芙山房荣获了“江西省五星级乡村民宿”称号，同时其村落式地快速发展也带动了村民增收，推动了乡村振兴。本案例基于管理者角色理论的框架，详细阐述了韩莉在不同阶段如何动态调整管理者角色，兼顾品牌价值提升、村民福祉改善与传统文化弘扬。通过本案例学习，旨在引导学员掌握企业家角色的基本概念，同时深化学员对共同富裕、文化自信、乡村振兴等领域管理实践思维的理解和运用。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Abstract: As China&#39;s Rural Revitalization Strategy advances in depth, rural tourism and the homestay industry have become important carriers for revitalizing the rural economy and inheriting traditional culture. Against this backdrop, this case study analyzes the management practices of Han Li, the owner of &quot;Zai fu shan fang&quot; homestay in Nanchang, Jiangxi Province, to explores how she achieved the transformation of &quot;Zai Fu Shan Fang&quot; from a single homestay into a village-scale homestay cluster with innovative formats through multi-stage strategic transitions. 
Zai Fu Shan Fang’s village-scale homestay cluster has been awarded the title of &quot;Five-Star Rural Homestay in Jiangxi Province&quot;. At the same time, its rapid development in a village-like manner has not only increased the income of the villagers but also promoted rural revitalization. This case is based on the framework of the Manager role theory. It elaborates in detail how Han Li dynamically adjusted her managerial roles at different stages, taking into account the enhancement of brand value, the improvement of villagers&#39; well-being, and the promotion of traditional culture. By studying this case, learners will grasp fundamental concepts of management roles while deepening their understanding and application of management practice thinking in areas such as common prosperity, cultural confidence, and rural revitalization.
</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《管理学》、《组织行为学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">管理者角色理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-10</td>
                            </tr>
